Package org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.fy23.gamepad2.teleop

Class TeleOpState

java.lang.Object
org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.fy23.gamepad2.teleop.TeleOpState
public class TeleOpState extends Object
Stores the state of the controls. The control scheme updates this, then the OpMode reads it. This effectively maps buttons to actions.
